1583377200.title: Fairly Normal
1583377200.descr: In this episode of Fairly Normal, Dane Reynolds lets us into his California home. Dane talks about how it felt to leave Quiksilver, he explains the process which led to him creating his own brand, Former, and reveals how it is possible to be a father, a husband and an entrepreneur while traveling the world as a professional surfer.

1583380800.title: Firsthand. 12-й сезон. 7-я серия - "Tom Wallisch"

1583409600.descr: CPH Open: Everyone is a Winner is a documentary produced by FUEL TV in partnership with Monster Energy, about the story behind the event celebrating the true essence of skateboarding

1583412300.title: HELride-2019
1583412300.descr: Fuel TV traveled to Helsinki Finland to attend one of the most iconic skateboarding celebration in Europe. An inner look at this competition which gathered each year more people from every part of the globe.

1583413200.title: The Search
1583413200.descr: What is it that makes us Explore? The restless urge to pack up and go. When the rumor of a perfect wave won't leave your mind. The anticipation, the laughs, the disasters, the surf. It defines who we are are... The Search.

1583416800.title: Shop Talk with Matt Biolos. Сезон 1. 2-я серия
1583416800.descr: Matt Biolos is one really singular shaper. Coming from a skateboarding and snowboarding background, this former punk artist made a name for himself in the shaping industry with his brand Lost Surfboards for over 30 years now. This Shop Talk episode is dedicated to him, his career, and his vision of surfing.

1583418000.title: Shop Talk with Jason Stevenson. Сезон 1. 1-я серия
1583418000.descr: Jason Stevenson, the head shaper and founder of JS - the brand with the recognizable tractor, spent some time in Portugal during which we caught up with him. We stole some of his time to talk about his career, his projects and his team.

1583419200.title: Taj Burrow: Life After The Tour
1583419200.descr: After almost two decades traveling the world, Taj Burrow was looking forward to the life away from the tour. Surfing the best waves he could find around West Oz, and spending time with his wife and daughter. That being said, the best surfer to never win a world title still enjoys the occasional getaway from Australia. This time the destination was the wave rich country of Portugal.

1583431200.title: Scratching the Surface
1583431200.descr: Scratching the Surface shows us the first steps of Julian Wilson in the surfing scene, since his very first wave until he became a world renowned and talented surfer.

1583434800.title: Thrillbillies. Сезон 3. 7-я серия - "Charity Work"
1583434800.descr: A non-fiction series, Thrillbillies follows the adventures and exploits of a series of reckless daredevils who throw caution to the wind and attempt ill-advised stunts and crazy dares. The two stars, Cam and Crum, often attach rockets to household furniture and attempt to ride that furniture as long as possible; in one episode, they successfully rode a rocket-propelled toilet. Cam and Crum are joined by a variety of "thrillbillies apprentices," who idolize their mentors and will attempt almost anything to gain their approval and respect. Many times this turns into an all-out competition between the apprentices to see who can successfully perform the wildest and most dangerous stunts. Thrillbillies is very popular among thrill seekers and people who enjoy finding creative uses for mundane objects. Many viewers also watch this program in hopes of seeing a serious accident, which has happened several times; these accidents often involve explosions, flying shrapnel, or flash fires.
